{"article_id":"oTsp2fgPlwTEpctl","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"A series of explosive memos","depth":9},{"id":2,"text":"prepared by former FBI director James Comey about his troubling encounters with President Trump","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"were released Thursday","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"and closely tracked Comey 's description of them in congressional testimony and in a new book","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"Comey has authored .","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"The memos ,","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"provided to Congress late Thursday ,","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"also had previously been provided to Justice special counsel Robert Mueller","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"to assist his investigation into Trump 's possible attempts","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"to obstruct the probe of Russia 's interference in the 2016 elections .","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"They detail the president 's alleged demands for loyalty from the former director and his requests","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"for Comey to shut down its investigation into former national security adviser Michael Flynn .","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"Flynn later pleaded guilty to lying to the FBI about his pre-inaugural contacts with Russia ambassador Sergey Kislyak .","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"Flynn is now cooperating with Mueller 's investigators .","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"Among the disclosures in the memos is a Feb. 8 , 2017 , encounter","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"in which Trump confronted Comey about the contents of a dossier","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"prepared by a former British intelligence agent","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"purportedly describing Trump 's involvement with prostitutes during a 2013 visit in Moscow .","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"`` The president brought up the 'Golden Shower Thing '","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"and said","depth":12},{"id":21,"text":"it really bothered him","depth":13},{"id":22,"text":"if his wife had any doubt about it , ''","depth":13},{"id":23,"text":"Comey said ,","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"recounting the conversation .","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"`` The president said","depth":12},{"id":26,"text":"that 'the hookers thing ' is nonsense","depth":12},{"id":27,"text":"but that","depth":12},{"id":28,"text":"( Russian President Vladimir ) Putin had told him","depth":13},{"id":29,"text":"'we have some of the most beautiful hookers in the world . ' ''","depth":13},{"id":30,"text":"Comey said","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"that he did not know","depth":13},{"id":32,"text":"when Trump had spoken with Putin ,","depth":13},{"id":33,"text":"but the timing of the account suggested","depth":13},{"id":34,"text":"that it was shortly after the dossier was made public in early January 2017 , just before Trump 's inauguration .","depth":13},{"id":35,"text":"At that same Feb. 8 meeting ,","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"which Comey also described in an interview with ,","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"Comey also recounted","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"having seriously crossed Trump","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"when he challenged the president 's comments to Fox News","depth":13},{"id":40,"text":"that Russia and America were similar","depth":14},{"id":41,"text":"in that both harbored `` killers . ''","depth":14},{"id":42,"text":"`` I do n't know what to make of it ,","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"but","depth":13},{"id":44,"text":"( Trump ) clearly noticed","depth":14},{"id":45,"text":"I had directly challenged him , ''","depth":14},{"id":46,"text":"Comey said in the memo .","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"At that point ,","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"Comey indicated in the interview ,","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"that he may have gone from potential ally to enemy of the president .","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"Trump tweeted","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"that the released memos `` show clearly","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"that there was NO COLLUSION and NO OBSTRUCTION . ''","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"Assistant Attorney General Stephen Boyd notified the chairs of at least six congressional committees","depth":6},{"id":54,"text":"that it was providing both redacted and un-redacted versions of the documents .","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"`` In light of the unusual events ... the department consulted relevant parties","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"and concluded","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"that the release of the memoranda at this time would not adversely impact any ongoing investigation or other confidentiality interests of the executive branch , ''","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"Boyd wrote .","depth":6},{"id":59,"text":"The release comes","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"as Comey ,","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"who was abruptly dismissed by Trump last year ,","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"is in the midst of a tour","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"promoting a book , Higher Loyalty : Truth , Lies , and Leadership ,","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"in which he details the encounters","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"memorialized in the memos .","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"Comey provided extensive testimony about the contents of the memos last year before the Senate Intelligence Committee .","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"Discussing the memos ' transfer to Congress in a Thursday interview with MSNBC ,","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"Comey said","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"he favored `` transparency . ''","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"The former FBI director said","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"he began memorializing his meetings and telephone contacts with the president from their first meeting , shortly before Trump 's inauguration .","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"Comey ,","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"who served three presidents ,","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"said","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"he took the unusual action","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"because he feared","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"Trump would `` lie '' about their interactions .","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"In an interview with","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"published earlier this week ,","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"Comey said","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"Trump was `` morally unfit '' to be president","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"and believed","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"that it was possible that Russia held compromising information on the president .","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"Rep. Elijah E. Cummings of Maryland , the senior Democrat on the House Committee on Oversight and Government Reform , said late Thursday","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"that Comey 's memos `` provide strong corroborating evidence of everything","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"he said about President Trump -","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"that the President wanted his personal loyalty ,","depth":13},{"id":88,"text":"that he wanted to end the Russia investigation ,","depth":14},{"id":89,"text":"and that he wanted Michael Flynn to walk . '' `` President Trump ' s interference was a blatant effort","depth":14},{"id":90,"text":"to deny justice ,","depth":12},{"id":91,"text":"and Director Comey was right","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"to document it","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"as it happened","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"- in real time , ''","depth":12},{"id":95,"text":"Cummings said in a statement .","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"The congressman added","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"that the memos are also `` corroborated by contemporaneous handwritten notes from top Justice Department official Dana Boente . ''","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"Boente is a former acting attorney general","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"who now serves as the FBI 's general counsel .","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"Cummings also notes","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"that the memo","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"that Comey gave to a friend","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"to read to the press about his Feb. 14 , 2017 , memo","depth":12},{"id":104,"text":"is marked as `` unclassified . ''","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"Comey 's critics have accused him of leaking classified information","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"when he shared that memo .","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"The chairmen of the three House committees","depth":8},{"id":108,"text":"that requested the documents from the Justice Department","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"said late Thursday","depth":7},{"id":110,"text":"they were glad","depth":7},{"id":111,"text":"Comey 's memos are finally being made public .","depth":7},{"id":112,"text":"`` These memos are significant for both what is in them and what is not , ''","depth":6},{"id":113,"text":"said a statement from Judiciary Chairman Bob Goodlatte , R-Va. , Oversight Chairman Trey Gowdy , R-S.C. , and Intelligence Chairman Devin Nunes , R-Calif .","depth":6},{"id":114,"text":"More :","depth":5},{"id":115,"text":"A minute-by-minute guide to 's exclusive interview with James Comey","depth":5},{"id":116,"text":"The Bubble :","depth":6},{"id":117,"text":"Conservatives and liberals agree","depth":7},{"id":118,"text":"James Comey 's book did n't do him any favors","depth":7},{"id":119,"text":"Related :","depth":6},{"id":120,"text":"James Comey on Trump :","depth":7},{"id":121,"text":"He tweets at me","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"'like the breakup","depth":9},{"id":123,"text":"he can ' t get over ' `","depth":9},{"id":124,"text":"` Former Director Comey 's memos show","depth":7},{"id":125,"text":"the President made clear","depth":8},{"id":126,"text":"he wanted allegations of collusion , coordination , and conspiracy between his campaign and Russia fully investigated , ''","depth":8},{"id":127,"text":"the chairmen said .","depth":6},{"id":128,"text":"`` The memos also made clear","depth":7},{"id":129,"text":"the 'cloud '","depth":10},{"id":130,"text":"President Trump wanted lifted","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"was not the Russian interference in the 2016 election cloud ,","depth":9},{"id":132,"text":"rather it was the salacious , unsubstantiated allegations","depth":12},{"id":133,"text":"related to personal conduct","depth":12},{"id":134,"text":"leveled in the dossier . '' The dossier ,","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"compiled by former British spy Christopher Steele","depth":13},{"id":136,"text":"and paid for by Democratic political committees ,","depth":13},{"id":137,"text":"included unsubstantiated allegations","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"that Trump interacted with prostitutes in a Moscow hotel room . `` The memos also show","depth":11},{"id":139,"text":"former Director Comey never wrote","depth":10},{"id":140,"text":"that he felt obstructed or threatened , ''","depth":10},{"id":141,"text":"the Republican congressmen wrote .","depth":6},{"id":142,"text":"The chairmen said","depth":5},{"id":143,"text":"the memos underscore","depth":7},{"id":144,"text":"that Comey had different standards","depth":9},{"id":145,"text":"in dealing with Trump","depth":9},{"id":146,"text":"than he did with others .","depth":8},{"id":147,"text":"He chose not to memorialize conversations with President Obama , Attorney General Lynch , Secretary Clinton , Andrew McCabe or others ,","depth":8},{"id":148,"text":"but `` he immediately began to memorialize conversations with President Trump , ''","depth":8},{"id":149,"text":"they said .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":299,"left":0,"right":298,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":298,"left":262,"right":297,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":262,"left":207,"right":261,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":207,"left":201,"right":206,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":201,"left":163,"right":200,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":163,"left":154,"right":162,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":154,"left":152,"right":153,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":152,"left":151,"right":3,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":151,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuc